title: See you at the Good Life Garden at 5pm. Pick up your name badge and enjoy the evening!
Registration is in front of the conference center until 10 a.m. and moves inside after 10.
Breakfast is served in Gallagher Hall.  Wear your badge to get your food!
Get fortified because sessions start at 8:45. Check your schedule for session location.
Make your way to Jackson Hall for Diane Bryant’s 10 a.m. keynote speech!
Vendor Fair opens in the Conference Center. Get your SWAG!
Lunch is served in Gallagher Hall starting at 11:30. Seating is available at the Alumni Center Moss Patio.
Fantastic door prize drawing in the Conference Center ballroom at 12:15. Must be present to win!
Don’t miss it! The Larry Sautter Award ceremony is at 4 p.m. at Jackson Hall in the Mondavi Center.
Fortify yourself! Breakfast is now being served in Gallagher Hall!
Vendor Fair is open in the Conference Center. Get your SWAG on!
Make your way to Jackson Hall for Andrew Isaacs’ keynote speech at 10 a.m.!
Catch the Lightning Talk by Jeané Blunt from UCOP. UCCSC is almost over, but Jeané will describe how you can connect and stay informed on all things UC IT year-round!
Lunch is ready and waiting for you at Gallagher Hall. Seating available at the Alumni Center Moss Patio.
Fantastic door prize drawing in the Conference Center ballroom at 12:15. Must be present to win!
Ice cream anyone? Look for the Davis Creamery ice cream cart in Gallagher Hall.
Thank you for coming to UCCSC 2018 and we hope to see you at UC Santa Barbara in July 2019!
